# ðŸ”¢ Number Conversion Guide

## Powers of 2 Reference

2^0 = 1 2^8 = 256
2^1 = 2 2^9 = 512
2^2 = 4 2^10 = 1024
2^3 = 8 2^11 = 2048
2^4 = 16 2^12 = 4096
2^5 = 32 2^13 = 8192
2^6 = 64 2^14 = 16384
2^7 = 128 2^15 = 32768






